data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER!! PRICE ADJUSTMENT! Beautiful Home in the Paloma Creek Community. Surrounded by parks, hiking trails, community amenities and swimming pools. This fantastic home features an open and spacious layout perfect for entertaining. LARGE Family Room with ceiling beams and lots of natural light. Gourmet Kitchen, SS Appliances, Vent-A-Hood, slide-in double oven, upgraded Quartz counters, glass tile mosaic backsplash and upgraded painted cabinets with soft close hinges! Formal dining with chair rail and picture frame molding; 4 Bedrooms-3 Baths, Spacious and private Office-Studio; Main Suite with a sitting area and charming Bay window. Main bath with over-sized shower and rain shower head, plus linen and walk-in closet. Game Room on the second floor. 8-foot Mahogany Glass and Iron front door; Short distance from schools, main highways, shopping and restaurants.
